{"id":257089,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/global-voices-智利：马普切犯人绝食抗议已经超过40天/","date":"2012-10-15T15:00:14Z","modified":"2012-10-15T15:00:14Z","title":"Global Voices | 智利：马普切犯人绝食抗议已经超过40天","content":"<blockquote>\n<p> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.emol.com/noticias/nacional/2012/10/04/563193/mapuche-cumplen-40-dias-en-huelga-de-hambre-en-la-araucania.html\">绝食抗议已经超过40天</a>。绝食抗议犯人的发言人表示，绝食者身体状况恶化，正承受不眠症、痉挛与肌肉酸痛这些症状。除了其它原因，绝食抗议的目的，主要是让大家注意到智利政府行使<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://indigenousnews.org/tag/antiterrorism-law/\">反恐怖主义法</a>的状况，以及<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A9%AC%E6%99%AE%E5%88%87%E4%BA%BA\">马普切人</a><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://ilovechile.cl/2012/10/01/mapuche-activists-to-enter-the-fifth-week-of-hunger-strike/68471\">取回祖先土地</a>的努力。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Ryan Seelau在<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://indigenousnews.org/2012/10/05/mapuche-hunger-strikers-reach-day-40-attorneys-argue-in-front-of-supreme-court/\">Indigenous News</a>的报导。</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/silvia-vinas/\" title=\"文章导读 Silvia Viñas\">Silvia Viñas</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/10/08/chile-mapuche-prisoners-on-hunger-strike-for-over-40-days/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2012/10/15/11705/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%99%BA%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%9A%E9%A9%AC%E6%99%AE%E5%88%87%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%BB%9D%E9%A3%9F%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8740%E5%A4%A9&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F10%2F15%2F11705%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=